pt:Chunk_122_3 a ns1:chunk ;
    pt:describes pt:Topic_10 ;
    ns1:text """2.0 Scope

This policy applies to all research activities involving the collection, analysis, and storage of digital and physical research data conducted by University staff, postgraduate research students enrolled on a research degree, visiting or emeritus staff, associates, holders of honorary and clinical contracts, contractors and consultants and others working on the University premises or carrying out research activity in the name, or on behalf of the University of Salford, and across all subject disciplines and fields of study, hereafter referred to as ‚ÄòResearchers‚Äô.

The policy does not apply to postgraduate taught students or undergraduates, but best research practice is recommended, and support and guidance is available to everyone."""^^xsd:string .

