    pt:describes pt:Topic_2 ;
    ns1:text """Researchers need to be aware of best practice measures for personal data collection, handling, security and sharing (including the appropriate deployment of anonymisation and related techniques and the creation of codebooks for their accompanying datafiles (e.g. a .txt file) so that data can be used/understood by third parties).

